{"ts": "2026-06-07T22:52:20.361928+00:00", "update": {"model": {"messages": [{"type": "ai", "data": {"content": "Here are every CIFAR-10 model implemented in this repository, along with its reported accuracy. The accuracy figures come directly from the README's benchmark table. Note that the `models/` directory contains implementation files for additional architectures (EfficientNet, GoogLeNet, LeNet, ShuffleNet, etc.) that don't appear in the README's reported results—only the models with published accuracy are listed below.\n\n| Model             | Reported Accuracy |\n|-------------------|-------------------|\n| VGG16             | 92.64%            |\n| ResNet18          | 93.02%            |\n| ResNet50          | 93.62%            |\n| ResNet101         | 93.75%            |\n| RegNetX_200MF     | 94.24%            |\n| RegNetY_400MF     | 94.29%            |\n| MobileNetV2       | 94.43%            |\n| ResNeXt29(32x4d)  | 94.73%            |\n| ResNeXt29(2x64d)  | 94.82%            |\n| SimpleDLA         | 94.89%            |\n| DenseNet121       | 95.04%            |\n| PreActResNet18    | 95.11%            |\n| DPN92             | 95.16%            |\n| DLA               | 95.47%            |\n\nThe `models/` directory also contains implementations for **EfficientNet**, **GoogLeNet**, **LeNet**, **MobileNet (V1)**, **PNASNet**, **SENet**, **ShuffleNet**, and **ShuffleNetV2**, but the README does not report CIFAR-10 accuracy numbers for those architectures.", "additional_kwargs": {"refusal": null}, "response_metadata": {"token_usage": {"completion_tokens": 581, "prompt_tokens": 9799, "total_tokens": 10380, "completion_tokens_details": {"accepted_prediction_tokens": null, "audio_tokens": 0, "reasoning_tokens": 156, "rejected_prediction_tokens": null, "image_tokens": 0}, "prompt_tokens_details": {"audio_tokens": 0, "cached_tokens": 2368, "cache_write_tokens": 0, "video_tokens": 0}, "cost": 0, "is_byok": true, "cost_details": {"upstream_inference_cost": 0.0012